
{{lowercase|title=p53 p63 p73 家族}}
'''p53 p63 p73 家族''' 是一个[[肿瘤抑制基因|抑癌基因]]家族<ref name="pmid10769197">{{cite journal |author=Levrero M, De Laurenzi V, Costanzo A, Gong J, Wang JY, Melino G |title=The p53/p63/p73 family of transcription factors: overlapping and distinct functions |journal=J. Cell. Sci. |volume=113 |issue= 10|pages=1661–70 |pmid=10769197 |doi= |url=http://jcs.biologists.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=10769197|date=May 2000}}</ref><ref name="Finch2007">{{cite book|author=Caleb Ellicott Finch|title=The biology of human longevity: inflammation, nutrition, and aging in the evolution of lifespans|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=4rGOLEOC4mEC&pg=PA350|accessdate=23 December 2010|year=2007|publisher=Academic Press|isbn=978-0-12-373657-4|pages=350–}}</ref>

包括：

* [[p53|p53]]
* [[TP63|TP63]]（也被称为"p63"）
* [[p73|p73]]

有时候也简称为“p53家族”<ref name="pmid18627398">{{cite journal |author=Chen S, Moroi Y, Urabe K, ''et al.'' |title=Differential expression of two new members of the p53 family, p63 and p73, in extramammary Paget's disease |journal=Clin. Exp. Dermatol. |volume= 33|issue= 5|pages= 634–40|pmid=18627398 |doi=10.1111/j.1365-2230.2008.02851.x|date=July 2008}}</ref>。

== p53家族的进化关系 ==
p53、p63与p73不但在结构与功能上相似，在进化上也有相关性。整个p53家族都是从[[无脊椎动物|无脊椎动物]]的p63/p73祖先基因中进化而来<ref name="Levine et al. 2010">{{cite journal |author=Levine, A. J., V. A. Belyi, P. Ak, E. Markert, H. J. Wang, W. W. Hu, and A. Puzio-Kuter.'' |title=The origins and evolution of the p53 family of genes |journal=Cold Spring Harbor Perspectives in Biology|volume=2|year=2010}}</ref>。p53最早在[[软骨鱼|软骨鱼]]基因组的p63/p73[[基因重複|基因重複]]中分化出来<ref name="Levine et al. 2010" />，p63/p73此后在[[硬骨鱼|硬骨鱼]]中再分化为p63和p73<ref name="Levine et al. 2010" />。后来它们各自发展出了不同的结构与功能，最终形成了可以区分的三个基因—[[TP63|TP63]]、[[p73|p73]]、[[p53|p53]]。

